         <abstract>
            <p>The record is to be used for an early collection of texts on archangels, so far attested by two
               manuscripts only: <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML1835">EMML 1835</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML1841">EMML 1841</ref>, both from  the
               library of Dabra Ḥayq ʾƎsṭifānos.  However fragments of it are found in other homiliaries on archangels such as <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1295Dersan">Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel</ref>.
               The compilation may have been inspired by <ref type="pers" corresp="PRS10626ZaraY">Zarʾa Yāʿqob</ref>.</p>
         </abstract> 
